## Test Specification

### `tests/unit/test_config.py`

```
Settings loading and defaults
- Settings loads from .env without error when all required keys present
- Missing GEMINI_API_KEY → ValidationError
- Missing ANTHROPIC_API_KEY → ValidationError
- Missing DATABASE_URL → ValidationError
- PIPELINE_VERSION not set → defaults to "v1"
- QUALITY_THRESHOLD not set → defaults to 7.0
- HUMAN_REVIEW_ENABLED not set → defaults to True
- MAX_ITERATION_ATTEMPTS not set → defaults to 7

Settings validation
- HUMAN_REVIEW_URGENCY_MINIMUM="low"    → valid
- HUMAN_REVIEW_URGENCY_MINIMUM="medium" → valid
- HUMAN_REVIEW_URGENCY_MINIMUM="high"   → valid
- HUMAN_REVIEW_URGENCY_MINIMUM="urgent" → ValidationError
- PIPELINE_VERSION="v1" → valid
- PIPELINE_VERSION="v2" → valid
- PIPELINE_VERSION="v3" → valid
- PIPELINE_VERSION="v4" → ValidationError
- QUALITY_THRESHOLD=0.9 → ValidationError (must be >= 1.0)
- QUALITY_THRESHOLD=10.1 → ValidationError (must be <= 10.0)
```
